-Jenny! Jenny Fox!

1396
01:20:09,959 --> 01:20:11,583
Sim.

1397
01:20:11,667 --> 01:20:13,166
Que bom ver você.

1398
01:20:13,250 --> 01:20:16,291
-Olá, Dr. G.
-Jenny Fox.

